ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真唔真，咁我心都定啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呃你有金執咩<br />\n我第2take 天光道靠背壟pass<br />\n唔洗上常盛街呀<br />\n講你又唔信<br />\n乜柒掉頭泊車斜路起步都唔洗做"},{"pid":"7159bb74f77c35550b4284c4ca2e39418d56cb06","tid":352982,"uid":16978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T15:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果只考丙部，係未唔會叫你係斜路停低再開車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗三手調頭同斜路停車<br />\n就咁跟條線行一圈就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真唔真，咁我心都定啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呃你有金執咩<br />\n我第2take 天光道靠背壟pass<br />\n唔洗上常盛街呀<br />\n講你又唔信<br />\n乜柒掉頭泊車斜路起步都唔洗做</blockquote><br />\nsame<br />\n我第2 take 天光道亞皆老街pass<br />\n冇考調頭"},{"pid":"353b109562f9293b61e60b9afafce539354ae861","tid":352982,"uid":91309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:28:31.000Z","msg":"不用 第二次考加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 天光道係比其他路有點麻煩"},{"pid":"531b9a3118b5ce1374587982a2e79758104eb4a0","tid":352982,"uid":128414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不用 第二次考加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 天光道係比其他路有點麻煩</blockquote><br />\n我覺得天光道 暑假 算幾好考<br />\n只係自己on9 心急 <br />\n前面塞車 排左係亞皆老街燈位第一個<br />\n點知前面郁得少少<br />\n跟住佢郁 停撚左係行人過路線到 肥左"},{"pid":"3f2707ef59ac1b98e88cd7b207abfe15fc578b0d","tid":352982,"uid":128414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:34:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不用 第二次考加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 天光道係比其他路有點麻煩</blockquote><br />\n我覺得天光道 暑假 算幾好考<br />\n只係自己on9 心急 <br />\n前面塞車 排左係亞皆老街燈位第一個<br />\n點知前面郁得少少<br />\n跟住佢郁 停撚左係行人過路線到 肥左</blockquote><br />\n我7月考第一次肥丙 黎緊下星期再考<br />\n好彩抽番天光道 未開學"},{"pid":"d2669004e56e7cef2fc67b0e1a19f37d2408b379","tid":352982,"uid":16978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:39:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不用 第二次考加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 天光道係比其他路有點麻煩</blockquote><br />\n我覺得天光道 暑假 算幾好考<br />\n只係自己on9 心急 <br />\n前面塞車 排左係亞皆老街燈位第一個<br />\n點知前面郁得少少<br />\n跟住佢郁 停撚左係行人過路線到 肥左</blockquote><br />\n我7月考第一次肥丙 黎緊下星期再考<br />\n好彩抽番天光道 未開學</blockquote><br />\n未必考返轉右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1f3cb1e2bbd0e0d9cf09db89d9a6f3e7ce483a","tid":352982,"uid":74495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:43:46.000Z","msg":"下星期考 有無咩要特別注意 唔想再肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個師傅話入試場 入左啲可以踩極力子咁行 其實得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e435c8d22c6f38a5904b08932be93eec6f4e6b7","tid":352982,"uid":16978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下星期考 有無咩要特別注意 唔想再肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個師傅話入試場 入左啲可以踩極力子咁行 其實得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我師傅教 先係試場門口睇紅區有冇路人踩入去/即將入去<br />\n冇既先1波入去 轉個彎對正試場4號停車位 <br />\n到左你既右手邊地下停車金屬釘先拎軚轉右就okay<br />\n途中佢教埋我返試場前要搵機會上一次3波踩上30跟住收油-&gt;2波-&gt;1波<br />\n完成"},{"pid":"18a0a6f862e0fbe190edd25da8469ffdf376b179","tid":352982,"uid":16978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T15:54:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下星期考 有無咩要特別注意 唔想再肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個師傅話入試場 入左啲可以<span style=\"color: red;\">踩極力子</span>咁行 其實得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我師傅教 先係試場門口睇紅區有冇路人踩入去/即將入去<br />\n冇既先1波入去 轉個彎對正試場4號停車位 <br />\n到左你既右手邊地下停車金屬釘先拎軚轉右就okay<br />\n途中佢教埋我返試場前要搵機會上一次3波踩上30跟住收油-&gt;2波-&gt;1波<br />\n完成</blockquote><br />\n最好唔好"},{"pid":"70cd0e5ae8a7a3e144638b9ffca97942d4559687","tid":352982,"uid":74495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下星期考 有無咩要特別注意 唔想再肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個師傅話入試場 入左啲可以踩極力子咁行 其實得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我師傅教 先係試場門口睇紅區有冇路人踩入去/即將入去<br />\n冇既先1波入去 轉個彎對正試場4號停車位 <br />\n到左你既右手邊地下停車金屬釘先拎軚轉右就okay<br />\n途中佢教埋我返試場前要搵機會上一次3波踩上30跟住收油-&gt;2波-&gt;1波<br />\n完成</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次學車試下 本身都覺得1波入去好啲 快期搵左另一個師傅好hea 希望今次pass到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b268b7dccd3e65120032ef368f722c5a0b7d000","tid":352982,"uid":18988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T22:38:00.000Z","msg":"係唔係有條路線有工程改左路"},{"pid":"89cdac969f4779e07acb2d5cfca0eff1f4de1292","tid":352982,"uid":118131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:07:56.000Z","msg":"唔信就問你師傅. 3手, 斜路, 泊位 係乙部.<br />\n丙就行一轉<br />\n<br />\n樓主我同你一樣, 第1次pass 乙, 之後係咁問師傅做乜練3手同斜路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不話天光道係我路試fail 既地方, 樓主加油.<br />\n<br />\n轉右係天堂. 轉左就... good luck"},{"pid":"495c0f0f627c5519b0033d1bf1cb8f49c71fd17b","tid":352982,"uid":118131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T13:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下星期考 有無咩要特別注意 唔想再肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個師傅話入試場 入左啲可以踩極力子咁行 其實得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你由出車去到車場口,可以踩盡極力子唔洗鬆, 但一出車場就要鬆架喇<br />\n<br />\n利申. 考過天光道"},{"pid":"52ce05952486c249b75be07c136a56c46f44be9b","tid":352982,"uid":128414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T15:21:37.000Z","msg":"聽日重考丙 跪求合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}